---
import Container from "../../primitives/Container.astro";
---
<section class="bg-white" aria-labelledby="solar-intro-title">
  <Container>
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24 reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Full-lifecycle solar EPC</p>
      <h2 id="solar-intro-title" class="fluid-h2 mt-3">From rooftop to utility-scale — engineered to perform.</h2>
      <p class="fluid-lead mt-5 text-muted">
        Empereal delivers complete solar PV solutions across all scales. We design, engineer, procure, construct, commission, and maintain high-performance systems — from distributed rooftop and carport installations to multi-megawatt utility-scale solar farms.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-5 text-base leading-relaxed text-muted sm:text-lg">
        With over 1.2 GW of solar PV capacity delivered and 350+ projects successfully completed, we deliver bankable, grid-compliant solar generation that meets stringent regulatory requirements and long-term performance targets in challenging environments.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
